<!-- javax.baja.sys.BajaException.toString(javax.baja.sys.Context) -->
<method name="toString"  public="true">
<annotation><type class="java.lang.Override"/>
</annotation>
<description>
Implementation of the &lt;code&gt;Localizable&lt;/code&gt; interface. If this exception&#xa; wraps another &lt;code&gt;Localizable&lt;/code&gt; exception, then return the localized&#xa; message of that wrapped exception. Otherwise, let the JVM attempt to&#xa; do its own localization by returning &lt;code&gt;getLocalizedMessage()&lt;/code&gt;.
</description>
